3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a new algorithm for distributed stochastic gradient training that involves error-compensated compression. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper discusses convergence rates and speedup in the proposed algorithm.
